		<label>Ravager</label>
		<description>The dreaded auto mortar was not enough to sate the mechanoids’ hunger for destruction. Their solution? The ravager, a mobile artillery emplacement. Able to charge excess energy in its reserve power cells, it can temporarily overcharge its cannon and launch a shell that splits into three destructive blasts while still in flight.</description>
